Class User

java.lang.Object
  ca.ubc.magic.icd.web.model.MagicItem
      ca.ubc.magic.icd.web.model.User

public class User
extends MagicItem

A basic object that extends MagicItem which stores information related to users Adds username, exp, points, imageURL, a list of friends and a list of bits.

Author:
Jeffrey Payan, Stephen Kidson
